x >0,\,x\neq 1,
\sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac {x^{3^n}+(x^{3^n})^2} {1-x^{3^{n+1}}}
\displaystyle \frac{u+u^2}{1-u^3} = \frac{1}{1-u} - \frac{1}{1-u^3}
\sum_{n=0}^N \frac {x^{3^n}+(x^{3^n})^2} {1-x^{3^{n+1}}} = \sum_{n=0}^N \left( \frac{1}{1-x^{3^{n}}} - \frac{1}{1-x^{3^{n+1}}}\right) =\frac{1}{1-x^{3^0}} - \frac{1}{1-x^{3^{N+1}}} 
\sum_{n=0}^{\infty} \frac {x^{3^n}+(x^{3^n})^2} {1-x^{3^{n+1}}} = \frac{1}{1-x} - \lim_{N\to\infty}\frac{1}{1-x^{3^{N+1}}} = \frac{1}{1-x} -  \begin{cases} 1, & |x| < 1\\ \frac12 & x = -1\\ \text{undefined}, & x = 1\\ 0, & |x| > 1\\ \end{cases}
